	color = { 0 0 0 }
	color2 = { 255 255 255 }
	capital = c_Kyrelapetra

	can_create = {
			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

	ai_primary_priority = {
		if = {
			limit = {
				culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}

e_Malmadmos = {
	color = { 109 53 12 }
	color2 = { 255 255 255 }
	capital = c_Onoricdus

	can_create = {
			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

	ai_primary_priority = {
		if = {
			limit = {
				culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}

e_Gourngythieia = {
	color = { 195 62 17 }
	color2 = { 255 255 255 }
	capital = c_Kynkorinlia

	can_create = {
			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

	ai_primary_priority = {
		if = {
			limit = {
				culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}

e_Nymagrinlia = {
	color = { 180 191 20 }
	color2 = { 255 255 255 }
	capital = c_Itankameieia

	can_create = {
			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

		if = {

		color = { 178 63 36 }

			NOT = {
				faith = {
					religion_tag = christianity_religion

	color = { 227 168 27 }
	color2 = { 255 255 255 }

	can_create = {
			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

	ai_primary_priority = {
		if = {
			limit = {
				culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}

e_Artemporlia = {
	color = { 136 128 35 }
	color2 = { 255 255 255 }
	capital = c_Megaloitosse

	can_create = {
			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

	ai_primary_priority = {
		if = {
			limit = {
				culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}

	k_Kaamaium = {
		color = { 136 128 35 }

		capital = c_Megaloitosse

		can_create = {
			NOT = {
				faith = {
					religion_tag = christianity_religion
					has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
				}
			}
		}

		ai_primary_priority = {
			if = {
				limit = {
					culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
				}
				add = @correct_culture_primary_score
			}
		}

		d_Artemporlia = {
			color = { 136 128 35 }
			color2 = { 255 255 255 }

			capital = c_Megaloitosse

			c_Megaloitosse = {
				color = { 136 128 35 }
				color2 = { 255 255 255 }

				b_Megaloitosse = {
					province = 7422

					color = { 136 128 35 }
					color2 = { 255 255 255 }

				}
			}
		}

e_Kallikouera = {
	color = { 50 50 50 }
	color2 = { 255 255 255 }
	capital = c_Opumetaporias

	can_create = {
			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

	ai_primary_priority = {
		if = {
			limit = {
				culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}

	k_Agrincarymos = {
		color = { 50 50 50 }

		capital = c_Opumetaporias

		can_create = {
			NOT = {
				faith = {
					religion_tag = christianity_religion
					has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
				}
			}
		}

		ai_primary_priority = {
			if = {
				limit = {
					culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
				}
				add = @correct_culture_primary_score

e_Agrincarymos = {
	color = { 184 155 84 }
	color2 = { 255 255 255 }
	capital = c_Didamphicum

	can_create = {
			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

	ai_primary_priority = {
		if = {
			limit = {
				culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}
